{"word":"Lameness","slug":"lameness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Lameness</b> Disqualified priests from exercising the priestly office<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=18'>Lev 21:18</a><br/> Disqualified animals for sacrificial uses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=21'>Deu 15:21</a><br/> Hated by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=8'>2Sa 5:8</a><br/> Healed by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=5'>Mat 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=31'>Mat 15:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=14'>Mat 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=22'>Luk 7:22</a><br/> Healed by Peter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3&verse=11'>Act 3:11</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=13'>Heb 12:13</a>"}]}